posting_body: ['Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 86', 'OR Text', '86', 'to', 'show contact info', 'for more information.', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1374 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Meet Pike Motorworks, the next chapter of the Pike/Pine renaissance, offering über-luxurious apartments and unrivaled amenities.', 'Every detail has been designed to preserve the site’s historic origins and celebrate The Hill’s effortless individuality, from the urban art sculpture in the courtyard to the building’s original 1926 auto row façade.', 'This is your chance to live at the intersection of classic Seattle and right now.', 'Features:', 'Gourmet kitchens with striking custom cabinets, Extra-large custom closets, Abundant natural light, Grand vaulted ceilings, Spacious floor plans, Expansive insulated windows, Under-cabinet dimmable LED kitchen lighting, Wood-style plank flooring, Spacious walk-in tiled showers*, Stunning black ceramic tile back-splashes, Energy-efficient GE stainless steel appliances, Premium hardware, fixtures and finishes throughout, Reclaimed wood doors, Quartz counter-tops', '*Select Units', 'Community Amenities:', 'Pet decks, Redhook Brewpub, Paw wash station, Original repurposed materials, Accelerate business center, Urban art sculpture, Station lounge, Vibrant retail courtyard, RPM fitness center, Sunroof deck', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet friendly!', 'Please contact us for details.', 'Want more information?', 'Follow this link:', '<URL>', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', 'Y5Pjsy4vbvI']
